Package: sparkmon
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Leo Kozlowski <leonkozlowski@anomalyco.com>
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/leonkozlowski/sparkmon
Description: Terminal-based monitoring dashboard for NVIDIA DGX Spark clusters
 Sparkmon provides a real-time terminal UI for monitoring multi-node DGX
 Spark clusters by polling node_exporter and dcgm-exporter metrics.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time CPU, memory, disk, and network monitoring
  - GPU utilization, temperature, and memory tracking
  - Side-by-side cluster visualization
  - No browser or external dependencies required
 .
 Useful for monitoring DGX Spark cluster infrastructure,
 debugging performance issues, and visualizing cluster health.